                <h3 class="font-bold text-red-900 mb-2">Cons</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-5 text-sm text-red-900 space-y-1">
                  <li>7B model — significant capability gap vs frontier</li>
                  <li>No public pricing — enterprise quote only</li>
                  <li>Cohere merger not yet closed — roadmap uncertainty</li>
                  <li>No mainland China service</li>
                  <li>Developer docs oriented to enterprise buyers</li>
                  <li>Smaller community than OpenAI/Anthropic/Mistral</li>
                  <li>No Chat Completions endpoint (Responses API only)</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
